src = run_commad_and_save_output_to_file(['python3', '-m',
    'oval_graph.command_line', 'arf-to-json', '--all',
    'tests/test_data/ssg-fedora-ds-arf.xml', '_package_\\w+_removed'])
time.sleep(5)
subprocess.check_call(['python3', '-m', 'oval_graph.command_line',
    'arf-to-json', '--all', 'tests/test_data/ssg-fedora-ds-arf.xml',
    '_package_\\w+_removed', '-o' + src])
with open(src, 'r') as f:
    rules = json.load(f)
assert len(rules.keys()) == 4
